<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Million Seconds Club</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Million Seconds Club</h1>
        <p>Find out when your millionth second birthday is!</p>
        
        <form action="/calculate" method="post">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="date">Date of Birth:</label>
                <input type="date" id="date" name="date" required>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="time">Time of Birth:</label>
                <input type="time" id="time" name="time" required>
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit">Calculate</button>
        </form>
        
        <div class="info">
            <h2>What is a Million Second Birthday?</h2>
            <p>A million seconds is approximately 11.6 days. Your millionth second birthday 
               occurs exactly 1,000,000 seconds after you were born.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
